data.description: This beautiful 3 bedroom, 2 bath, one story home sits on a corner lot and features one of the larger yards in Solana Ridge! This ready for move in home features a great floorplan for entertaining, upgraded flooring with a split floorplan and won't last long. Close to shopping, restaurants, schools and highways for an easy commute.
